      <section>
        <h2>Chair Model Fit by Height: Gesture vs Leap Plus vs Aeron</h2>
        <p>
          Mapping those requirements to the three most-recommended ergonomic chairs for tall users.
          Specs used: Gesture (seat height 15–21", seat depth 15.75–18.75", back height 24");
          Leap Plus (seat height 15.5–22.5", seat depth 15.75–19.75", back height 25.5");
          Aeron Size C (seat height 16–20.5", seat depth fixed 18.5", back height ~22").
          For tall-user fit details on each model, see the
