              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-secondary/20">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted-foreground font-medium">6'6"+"</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted-foreground"><strong class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-400">No Fit</strong> — seat height and depth both below requirement</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-muted-foreground"><strong class="text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-400">Borderline</strong> — height 22.5" is marginal; depth 19.75" short for 21"+ thigh needs</td>
